{"tid":611501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"換屆選舉　建制策略坐二望三","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T09:01:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"613f865e5904772ca0deb0bb4cb71ad1c0be1e0f","tid":611501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180331/20348511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F20348511&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d42cdfdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F20348511&h=b9abdb61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180331/20348511</a><br />\n<br />\n換屆選舉　建制策略坐二望三<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180331/large/18566188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180331%2Flarge%2F18566188.jpg&h=7d99e591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔣麗芸稱經過補選後，建制派在九西可做到「坐二望三」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】<br />\n<br />\n建制派在九西「零的突破」，2020年立會換屆選舉時建制派能否保住鄭泳舜攻下的議席？蔣麗芸稱建制派策略是坐二望三，但若最後為減風險，只求保兩席，而民建聯只能派一張名單出戰，屆時由老將蔣麗芸或新丁鄭泳舜擔大旗勢成焦點。<br />\n<br />\n現有6個議席的九西選區於前年大選時，民主派取4席，建制派僅取兩席。隨着青年新政游蕙禎及無政黨劉小麗被DQ，經過早前補選，民主派剩下兩席，建制派佔3席。單以總得票計算，手執約10.2萬票的建制派似乎有力取得3個議席，以前年選舉而言，6名勝選人中得票最少的游蕙禎僅兩萬餘票，而九西每席當選門檻是總票數約17%、即逾4.7萬票，現時只有蔣麗芸及梁美芬得票高於這門檻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬：難複製補選戰果<br />\n<br />\n外界關注換屆選舉時，民建聯會否由蔣麗芸及鄭泳舜各自出戰，若梁美芬爭取連任，則建制派有3張名單，一旦分票不均隨時陰溝裏翻船。被問及2020年大選如何部署，蔣直言經過今次補選，建制派可做到坐二望三，但承認要平分這10萬多票有難度，否則若穩陣起見，只能守住現有兩席。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬也指不能因補選結果過於高興，尤其大選時民主派可作不同部署，未必能複製今次戰果，認為至少要再觀察下次九西補選情況，才能考慮建制派是否可派3張名單出戰。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t建制贏九西議席「歸功」泛民：　姚松炎未保本<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"ccb598d3a7df15cc4936194dfcbad9403a954aa6","tid":611501,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"有關sir無難度"},{"pid":"33700f81c57aa05a79672c82cad463ebdc7a28ad","tid":611501,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdf7dcb7c852388e152abc8582c632df35888b60","tid":611501,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"33700f81c57aa05a79672c82cad463ebdc7a28ad","tid":611501,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"又係呢個借口既然係咁你唔屌走保皇狗？<br />\n一樣但放生保皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0213ea37e8b4ac80d2b3fe21040b0fb9e63c5856","tid":611501,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccb598d3a7df15cc4936194dfcbad9403a954aa6","tid":611501,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"有關sir無難度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"又想屈白票撚係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2fcec9ffca309c9dc8fbd536b2e90078b48ebf","tid":611501,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cdf7dcb7c852388e152abc8582c632df35888b60","tid":611501,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"33700f81c57aa05a79672c82cad463ebdc7a28ad","tid":611501,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"又係呢個借口既然係咁你唔屌走保皇狗？<br />\n一樣但放生保皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"有泛民打手樓主LIKLN加五毛狙擊手<br />\n打壓本土冇難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06612e3d125ecfb1c927745ba943e39a5bf1cd06","tid":611501,"uid":385